milestones.description: Staple and Steve Massiah's 6-run partnership is USA's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 3 between Staple and Alexander
Nasir Javed and Johnson's 12-run partnership is USA's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 5 between Rashid and Johnson
Gilchrist has broken the record for most sixes (86) in ODIs for AUS, going past Ricky Ponting's 85
Aijaz Ali has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (2) for USA, going past Alexander
